{"type": "article", "id": 25702, "title": "折叠边桌", "description": "", "date": "2016-04-20T07:00:15Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 20, "image": "img/article/article_show/2016070213082314fM7yBzGAwTp8bQ.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是一张可折叠的边桌，用橡木做的。圆桌面下是十字交叉的桌腿，将它折叠在一个平面后，圆桌的两侧木板也可以顺势垂下来，最后收成一个可以悬挂的桌子，很方便。这种小巧而容易携带收纳的桌子适合小空间或者户外，有黑、黄、白和原木色四种，售价 99 美元，<a href=\"http://www.ta-bl.co.uk/\">这里是购买链接。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702130821pmk3Ko2Vbs1HSixJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.33666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021308222ai9uBPmcWvM7U1O.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.155\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016070213082298hSAmBqlgLJMKUn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.34\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}